hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: We used to work together toprol xl 100mg cost I wonder whether Hillary Clinton and her aide, Huma Abedin – the wife of disgraced Democratic New York mayoral candidate Anthony Weiner – ever talk about men. I don’t suppose they do. Scorn loses its power when expressed openly, woman to woman, turning the only dignified reaction to a philandering husband into something noxious and demeaning: a Ricki Lake “Wronged Women” special. No, I suspect they both react to their men much as they would to a dog cocking his leg on the living room carpet: by wincing and silently berating whoever allowed these incontinent mongrels into civilised society in the first place.
